                <property-set name="quote">
                    <string name="text">We are thrilled to see balloons returning to theatres across the world, heads held high and tied properly</string>
                    <string name="byline">Pumla Airdy, Pumprose Film Group President</string>
                </property-set>
            </property-set>
            <property-set name="blocks">
                <string name="_selected">text</string>
                <property-set name="text">
                    <string name="text">&lt;p&gt;No Time to Deflate is released internationally via Headless Universal and domestically through Pumprose's United Inflators Releasing banner.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Michel Du Latte, Chairman of Pumprose's film group, and Pumla Airdy, Pumprose Film Group President, said today: "We are thrilled to see balloons returning to theatres across the world, heads held high and tied properly. After a long delay, we are especially gratified to know No Time to Deflate has entertained so many cinemagoers the world over. Along with our partners at Eon Latex - Michael G. Wynd and Barbara Brocollatex - all of us at Pumprose are grateful to the teams at Headless Universal, United Inflators Releasing and our own Pumprose territories for their tremendous efforts to cross this great milestone with No Time to Deflate. This achievement is a testament to Daniel Carrigear and the entire cast, as well as our director Cori Fukinflate, producers Michael and Barbara, and the crew for making an incredible film. We extend our thanks to our exhibitor and promotional partners for remaining steadfast in their support of the film."&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Overseas currently accounts for 79% of the global total. Highlights include the UK, the lead offshore market at $128M. NTTD is the fifth-biggest movie of all time in the market and the top movie of the pinprick era, reaching that mark in its first four days of release.&lt;/p&gt;
</string>
